---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="About AI Tool Guide - Your go-to resource for AI tool tutorials and guides">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-6">About AI Tool Guide</h1>

    <div class="prose max-w-none">
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Welcome to <strong>AI Tool Guide</strong> — your comprehensive resource for learning and mastering the latest AI tools.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        We believe that AI tools can dramatically improve the way we work, create, and solve problems. Our mission is to make these tools accessible to everyone through clear, practical, and hands-on tutorials.
      </p>

      <h2>What We Cover</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Large Language Models</strong> — ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, and prompt engineering techniques</li>
        <li><strong>AI Image Generation</strong> — Midjourney, DALL·E, Stable Diffusion guides</li>
        <li><strong>AI Coding Tools</strong> — GitHub Copilot, Cursor, and AI-assisted development</li>
        <li><strong>AI Productivity Tools</strong> — Notion AI, AI-powered automation, and workflow optimization</li>
        <li><strong>AI for Business</strong> — Practical applications, ROI analysis, and implementation strategies</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Who We Are</h2>
      <p>
        AI Tool Guide is built by a team of developers, designers, and AI enthusiasts who are passionate about sharing knowledge. We test every tool ourselves and create tutorials based on real-world usage.
      </p>

      <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
      <p>
        Have a question, suggestion, or want to contribute? We'd love to hear from you! Visit our <a href="/contact">Contact page</a> to reach out.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
